      "value": "<p>At 6th level, you gain a magical benefit based on the totemic aspect of your choice. You gain a +2 to your choice of Constitution, Dexterity or Wisdom score. Your maximum for the chosen score is now 22. If you chose Wisdom then you also gain proficiency in Wisdom saving throws if you do not have it already.</p><blockquote><p><strong>Upon reaching this level, you will have to manually increase the appropriate ability score and saving throw proficiency (if applicable).  It is recommended that you edit this feature to note what changes were made to help track it.</strong></p></blockquote>",
